Class QueryResult

  • Object
    • QueryResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Object>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NeoEMFQueryResult

    public class QueryResult
extends Object
implements Iterable<Object>
    Wraps the result of a MogwaiQuery and provides information on the query execution.

    QueryResult implements Iterable to ease result processing in client applications.

    Author:
    Gwendal DANIEL

    • Field Detail

      • result

        protected List<Object> result
        Stores the result of the query computation.

        This collection is used regardless whether the result is multi-valued or single-valued.

      • computationTime

        protected long computationTime
        Stores the time needed to compute the result of the query.

        If the query result is an instance of Iterable it is iterated to create the QueryResult. This can be costly in Gremlin-based queries that are computed when they are iterated.

      • isSingleResult

        protected boolean isSingleResult
        Stores whether the query returned a single result.

      • gremlinScript

        protected String gremlinScript
        The textual representation of the computed query.

    • Constructor Detail

      • QueryResult

        public QueryResult(Object engineResult,
                   String gremlinQuery)
        Constructs a new QueryResult from the given engineResult and literal gremlinScript.

        Note: if engineResult is an instance of Iterable this constructor iterates it to wrap the results. In case of Gremlin-based queries this can be costly because GremlinPipeline content is computed when iterated.

        Parameters:
        engineResult - the result of the query computation
        gremlinQuery - the textual representation of the computed query

      • QueryResult

        public QueryResult(Object engineResult,
                   GremlinScript gremlinScript)
        Constructs a new QueryResult from the given engineResult and gremlinScript.

        Note: if engineResult is an instance of Iterable this constructor iterates it to wrap the results. In case of Gremlin-based queries this can be costly because GremlinPipeline content is computed when iterated.

        Parameters:
        engineResult - the result of the query computation
        gremlinScript - the GremlinScript element representing the root of the computed query

      • isSingleResult

        public boolean isSingleResult()
        Returns:

      • getResults

        public Collection<Object> getResults()
                              throws MogwaiCoreException
        Returns the result of the Mogwai query wrapped in a Collection.

        This method always returns a Collection, even if the query doesn't return any object. Use it instead of getResult() if the query result size is not known.

        Returns:
        the result of the Mogwai query wrapped in a Collection
        Throws:
        MogwaiCoreException

      • getResult

        public <T> T getResult()
                throws MogwaiCoreException
        Returns a casted value created from the single query result.

        Note: this method throws a MogwaiCoreException if the query returns more than one result, see instead.

        Type Parameters:
        T - the type to cast the result of the query
        Returns:
        a casted value created from the single query result
        Throws:
        MogwaiCoreException - if the query returns more than one result
        ClassCastException - if the result cannot be cast to <T>

      • resultSize

        public int resultSize()
        Returns the number of objects returned by the query.

        Note: this method returns 1 even if the query result contains only the null value.
